- ¡Dios mío!

1849
01:32:00,646 --> 01:32:01,855
¡Perdiste!

1850
01:32:02,397 --> 01:32:03,690
¡Das pena!

1851
01:32:04,566 --> 01:32:06,026
Genial.

1852
01:32:06,860 --> 01:32:09,488
